No Meal Left Behind.name: No Meal Left Behind
No Meal Left Behind.bonus: Every 24 hours, your lowest level Meal gets +1 Lv. This only works on Meals Lv 5 or higher, and doesn't trigger on days you don't play.

The Artifact Matrix.name: The Artifact Matrix
The Artifact Matrix.bonus: Extends the Laboratory Event Horizon, adding another bonus to connect to! In particular, a boost to Artifact Find Chance!

Level Exemption.name: Level Exemption
Level Exemption.bonus: Completely and utterly removes the UNDER-LEVELED bonus reduction of all stamps in your collection, now and forever. Amen.

The Crop Matrix.name: The Crop Matrix
The Crop Matrix.bonus: Yet again even further extends the Laboratory Event Horizon, adding another bonus to connect to! In particular, a boost to Crop Depot!

Essence Confetti.name: Essence Confetti
Essence Confetti.bonus: Adds a new bonus of +3% All Essence Gain per 10 items found after 1000 items, as shown at The Slab in World 5.

The Slab Matrix.name: The Slab Matrix
The Slab Matrix.bonus: Further extends the Laboratory Event Horizon, adding another bonus to connect to! In particular, a boost to all bonuses from the Slab!

Papa Blob's Quality Guarantee.name: Papa Blob's Quality Guarantee
Papa Blob's Quality Guarantee.bonus: Increases the Max Level of all cooking meals by +10. Better meals, better levels, Papa Blob's.

Revenge of the Pickle.name: Revenge of the Pickle
Revenge of the Pickle.bonus: Adds a new boss page to the left of World 1 in Deathnote. Each BoneJoePickle in your inventory counts as +1 Boss Deathnote Kill!

Reinforced Science Pencil.name: Reinforced Science Pencil
Reinforced Science Pencil.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to your crop scientist's Data Sheet! Specifically '+20% Total Damage' per Crop!

Science Pen.name: Science Pen
Science Pen.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to your crop scientist's Data Sheet! Specifically '1.02x Plant Evolution Chance in Gaming (multiplicative)' per Crop!

MSA Expander I.name: MSA Expander I
MSA Expander I.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to the Miniature Soul Apparatus in World 3, specifically Farming EXP!

The Spirit Matrix.name: The Spirit Matrix
The Spirit Matrix.bonus: Even further extends the Laboratory Event Horizon, adding another bonus to connect to! In particular, a boost to W6 Skill exp gain!

Chef Geustloaf's Cutting Edge Philosophy.name: Chef Geustloaf's Cutting Edge Philosophy
Chef Geustloaf's Cutting Edge Philosophy.bonus: Increases the Max Level of all cooking meals by +10 again! But oh hoho, you sir are no Chef Geustloaf! Good luck cooking to these LVs!

Shrine Collective Bargaining Agreement.name: Shrine Collective Bargaining Agreement
Shrine Collective Bargaining Agreement.bonus: Shrines no longer lose EXP when moved around, so you can finally bring those baddies out of retirement!

UNDER CONSTRUCTION.name: UNDER CONSTRUCTION
UNDER CONSTRUCTION.bonus: This bonus isn't out yet, so you cant buy it! Please come back in a few updates there'll be more floors to sneak up to as well!

Quick Ref Access.name: Quick Ref Access
Quick Ref Access.bonus: Adds the Sneaking skill to your QuickRef menu! Manage your Ninja Twins from anywhere!

Science Marker.name: Science Marker
Science Marker.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to your crop scientist's Data Sheet! Specifically '+8% Jade Coin Gain' per Crop!

NAME NEEDED.name: NAME NEEDED
NAME NEEDED.bonus: All Divinity Gods give 1.05x higher Blessing bonus (the passive bonus that affects all characters always) per God Rank.

Gaming to the MAX.name: Gaming to the MAX
Gaming to the MAX.bonus: All plant types in Gaming have +1 Max Evolution, but this one is 50,000x rarer than normal and will make you wonder if evolution is even real (it is)

Deal Sweetening.name: Deal Sweetening
Deal Sweetening.bonus: Earn +25% more Magic Beans from the mysterious Legumulyte bean merchant found in the Troll Broodnest map.

Supersized Gold Beanstacking.name: Supersized Gold Beanstacking
Supersized Gold Beanstacking.bonus: You can now drop a stack of 100,000 Gold Food to supersize it! This will obviously give a bigger bonus, and will even enlargen the food on the stalk!

Science Crayon.name: Science Crayon
Science Crayon.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to your crop scientist's Data Sheet! Specifically '+7% Shiny Pet Lv Up Rate and Pet Breeding Rate' per Crop!

MSA Expander II.name: MSA Expander II
MSA Expander II.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to the Miniature Soul Apparatus in World 3, specifically Jade Coin Gain!

Science Featherpen.name: Science Featherpen
Science Featherpen.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to your crop scientist's Data Sheet! Specifically '1.10x Cooking Speed (multiplicative)' per Crop!

Mob Cosplay Craze.name: Mob Cosplay Craze
Mob Cosplay Craze.bonus: Certain monsters in World 6 will now have a rare chance to drop Ninja Hats, but only the hats that your Ninja Twins have equipped.

Gold Food Beanstalk.name: Gold Food Beanstalk
Gold Food Beanstalk.bonus: Grows a giant beanstalk behind the ninja castle! Drop a stack of 10,000 Gold Food to add it with the beanstalk and permanently gain its bonus!

MSA Expander III.name: MSA Expander III
MSA Expander III.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to the Miniature Soul Apparatus in World 3, specifically All Essence Gain!

Jade Coin Magnetism.name: Jade Coin Magnetism
Jade Coin Magnetism.bonus: Adds a new bonus of +5% Jade Coin Gain per 10 items found after 1000 items, as shown at The Slab in World 5.

Charmed, I'm Sure.name: Charmed, I'm Sure
Charmed, I'm Sure.bonus: All your Ninja Twins can now equip two of the same charm at once!

Crop Depot Scientist.name: Crop Depot Scientist
Crop Depot Scientist.bonus: Employs a friendly scientist blobulyte to keep a Data Sheet of all the crops you've ever found!

Science Environmentally Sourced Pencil.name: Science Environmentally Sourced Pencil
Science Environmentally Sourced Pencil.bonus: Adds a new bonus type to your crop scientist's Data Sheet! Specifically '+15% Cash from Mobs' per crop found!
